Fuse Fabric
==============================

Fuse Fabric is a distributed configuration, management and provisioning system for using [Apache Karaf](http://karaf.apache.org/), [Apache ServiceMix](http://servicemix.apache.org/) and [Fuse](http://fusesource.com/) in a public or private cloud.

